On Tue, Feb 08/00, Ryan Honeyman <honeyman@...> wrote:
> Played around in Sky this last weekend. No server has done the Noble
> on Sword (Windmill) Island since the latest patch. Looks like
> Verant doesn't want players to go much further in the Plane.
> Basically, once you kill the fairies and princess, you're done
> unless you want to die a whole bunch.

Yup. It's looking like Sky was put in as an advertisement for the
expansion, not a usuable place for people who paid to play this game
now.
